race.description: Sealeys Springworks (N/P) Tg 5+W Series F Pr2 Divi
race.comment: IS HE HAPPY (8) produced a moderate effort last time when seventh at Broken Hill over 375m behind Croatian Comet (22.45) in a NG. Placed at his previous run. Better than last start and worth following up. JAJA DING DONG (1) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a win (23.30) there the start prior. Has ability and is one of the better chances. COMPTON TIG (5) box seated before sticking on well to finish 2.25 lengths away in third (23.46) at this track in a Other over 400m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Hard to beat again. CADILLAC GIRL (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
